fection for farming. Her passion is rooted in the late stages of her Synergy bond ranks, but she’s friendly and another one of \u003cem\u003ePhantom \u003c/em\u003e\u003cem\u003eX\u003c/em\u003e’s uniquely designed characters. Since her Synergy Bond takes place primarily in the in-game MMO \u003cem\u003eHarvest World Online\u003c/em\u003e, her Phantom Thief appearance is based on her virtual avatar instead of her authentic self.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhether you’re a Phantom thief veteran or a recruit, our guides will help you get the most out of your tenure. If you’re looking for more \u003cem\u003ePersona 5 The Phantom X\u003c/em\u003e guides, here are our guides explaining the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/guides/609063/persona-5-phantom-x-p5x-gacha-banners-pity-contracts\"\u003egacha banners\u003c/a\u003e, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/guides/609183/persona-5-phantom-x-p5x-classroom-answers-questions\"\u003eclassroom answers\u003c/a\u003e, and even the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/guides/609030/persona-5-phantom-x-p5x-canon-protagonist-name-change-how-to\"\u003eprotagonist’s canon name\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
